    {
      "type": "asciinema",
      "narration": "Start by running slash model-audit from Claude Code. You get a menu with four check types. Tier Check validates weight class within each provider. Task Fit checks if the right model handles each job. Cost Accuracy reviews token spend. Or run all checks at once.",
